WEBVTT

12:39.571 --> 12:46.425
For the last so many lectures, we have been saying

12:47.503 --> 12:50.639
that you cannot pay for God’s love.

12:50.639 --> 12:55.395
It makes me laugh sometimes.

12:56.371 --> 13:01.371
Human beings can never understand his love,

13:01.503 --> 13:05.223
because they live in a very limited sphere.

13:05.223 --> 13:09.154
His love is unlimited. His forgiveness is unlimited.

13:09.154 --> 13:16.916
Even this word “unlimited” and “infinite”, we do not understand

13:17.011 --> 13:20.811
because we have not known anything like that.

13:20.811 --> 13:22.931
And to say that something is genuine

13:23.451 --> 13:25.971
is also like certifying something that is genuine.

13:26.451 --> 13:28.303
You don’t need a certificate.

13:28.371 --> 13:31.546
Even that human beings don't understand.

13:32.891 --> 13:37.871
We live with artificiality,

13:38.491 --> 13:41.731
we try to find the truth,

13:41.731 --> 13:44.771
again we accept artificiality as truth.

13:45.331 --> 13:47.263
Again we go on fighting.

13:47.371 --> 13:49.851
Then we think this is the truth.

13:50.611 --> 13:53.277
Again that turns out to be something, artificial thing

13:53.277 --> 13:56.521
or some sort of a mental projection.

13:56.811 --> 14:04.114
All these limited endeavours of human beings

14:04.114 --> 14:07.703
and the experiences they have,

14:07.811 --> 14:12.451
made him so conditioned,

14:12.451 --> 14:18.250
that it is not easy to understand God.

14:18.691 --> 14:24.347
He made all this universe in his compassion and love.

14:24.347 --> 14:28.235
He created you as human beings, also in his compassion and love.

14:28.235 --> 14:29.995
He doesn’t need anything.

14:30.571 --> 14:32.611
But he loves.

14:33.531 --> 14:40.361
And you can’t understand a person who loves beyond any reason,

14:40.651 --> 14:47.642
without any reward, just love because for love’s sake.

14:47.891 --> 14:55.491
We can’t think of one human being like that, who can love only for love’s sake.

14:55.491 --> 15:00.660
Only after Realization, as you grow more and more,

15:00.660 --> 15:06.880
you realise that loving is the greatest joy.

15:07.903 --> 15:11.371
And then, you cannot think of money in relation to him.

15:11.571 --> 15:15.851
It's something, you'll say but, I think,

15:16.451 --> 15:20.743
even to say this, "We don't need money or we don't take money"

15:20.743 --> 15:25.345
itself is so low level.

15:25.771 --> 15:30.303
It's so, so much gross.

15:31.451 --> 15:37.969
Because money and all these concepts are your own.

15:38.771 --> 15:43.377
He didn't make this world to get any fruits out of it.

15:43.691 --> 15:45.331
Nothing.

15:45.731 --> 15:47.851
He just made it because he loved.

15:48.331 --> 15:49.531
He wanted to express His Love.

15:49.731 --> 15:53.182
Just to manifest that Love, he made this world.

15:53.451 --> 15:55.371
There’s nothing else expected

15:55.571 --> 16:00.651
and to put the human mind at that level is an impossibility, I find, in the beginning.

16:00.651 --> 16:05.411
But gradually they start understanding how forgiving he is,

16:05.411 --> 16:08.771
how kind he is, how nice he is.

16:08.771 --> 16:12.451
So the first problem I have to face in the West always

16:12.451 --> 16:16.571
even in Paris this was the problem that I faced

16:16.571 --> 16:21.808
was that human beings feel guilty.

16:22.371 --> 16:25.451
And this guilt is such a big problem in the West,

16:25.651 --> 16:27.451
I just don't understand.

16:27.691 --> 16:29.451
You see, why do you feel guilty so much,

16:29.651 --> 16:32.571
as that is one of the hurdles of Sahaja Yoga, I've seen,

16:32.771 --> 16:34.651
that people start feeling guilty.

16:34.851 --> 16:36.411
To such an extent,

16:36.611 --> 16:39.691
that they don't believe that they can get Realization.

16:40.371 --> 16:43.451
They think they are sinners born outright,

16:43.691 --> 16:46.851
permanently, branded as 'sinners',

16:47.651 --> 16:50.331
and they can never take their Realization.

16:50.531 --> 16:52.491
I mean, just they brand themselves.

16:52.771 --> 16:54.411
It's beyond self pity also,

16:54.611 --> 16:58.771
I would say it's even self-destructive.

16:58.771 --> 17:02.371
Today, I've taken up this subject of Left Vishuddhi,

17:02.571 --> 17:06.611
because I felt that I must one day speak on this subject,

17:06.811 --> 17:09.531
that this is absolutely,

17:10.851 --> 17:17.619
not inteligible to God that you are guilty. For what?

17:18.851 --> 17:21.651
Guilty for what are you?

17:21.851 --> 17:24.651
If you ask yourself, you'll say, "Oh, we are guilty,

17:24.851 --> 17:27.451
because we've crucified Christ" at the most.

17:27.651 --> 17:31.371
That is the maximum guilt a human being, let's say, on his head.

17:31.571 --> 17:39.231
"We crucified Christ, we tortured all the saints". All right.

17:39.891 --> 17:43.851
But by being guilty what do you get?

17:43.851 --> 17:47.651
Do you get Him back, can you go back and correct that situation?

17:47.851 --> 17:50.451
You cannot.

17:50.451 --> 17:54.651
But harping upon that, you do get into your subconscious mind.

17:54.651 --> 18:02.295
You get into a position where you are no more normal to receive the Love of God.

18:02.571 --> 18:05.531
You recede into a corner of your mind,

18:05.731 --> 18:07.451
which is darkness,

18:07.651 --> 18:09.851
which is ignorant, which is blindness,

18:10.691 --> 18:13.851
where you cannot receive that beautiful reign,

18:14.771 --> 18:21.250
that eternal flow that's coming in.

18:21.691 --> 18:24.331
You hide yourself, at the back,

18:24.531 --> 18:26.291
and then you say,

18:26.491 --> 18:27.851
"What about the sun?

18:28.491 --> 18:33.912
I cannot receive it because I don't deserve it."

18:35.451 --> 18:38.698
Behind all this ego orientation in the West -

18:38.698 --> 18:43.771
Oh, I think, I wish they were purely egoistical. They are not.

18:43.771 --> 18:50.607
All this ego recedes bac ,into that little pouch, what we call the 'guilt'.

18:51.651 --> 18:54.491
You say something to someone.

18:54.491 --> 18:56.891
It's saying that point, that stage,

18:57.371 --> 19:01.153
that, "I've said it. All right, I've said it. I can take the responsability, i's good."

19:01.153 --> 19:02.531
Not that.

19:02.531 --> 19:07.611
But you come back home, "Oh, I should not have said that".

19:07.611 --> 19:13.100
So you wobble between one kind of action into another kind,

19:13.371 --> 19:15.971
from say, into an aggressive

19:16.451 --> 19:19.731
to another one of a receding type

19:19.731 --> 19:21.851
And this wobbling really,

19:22.531 --> 19:24.611
is very, very troublesome.

19:24.811 --> 19:26.691
It can go on too much.

19:26.891 --> 19:29.371
The oscilation could be so much.

19:29.611 --> 19:32.571
that it can make you absolutely frantic,

19:32.771 --> 19:38.909
diffident, and sometimes, useless.

19:41.451 --> 19:43.371
On the contrary,

19:43.771 --> 19:45.771
God wants to find human beings,

19:46.331 --> 19:47.611
who are cheerful people,

19:47.811 --> 19:49.571
who are happy people,

19:49.771 --> 19:52.371
who are thankful to Him for His blessings.

19:54.771 --> 19:57.931
The most unhappy animal in this world,

19:58.411 --> 20:01.277
is the human being, can you believe that?

20:01.851 --> 20:05.691
Animals, don't know happiness and unhappiness, also a good point is.

20:07.811 --> 20:09.771
But the most unhappy human being,

20:09.971 --> 20:12.571
and the most complicated human being,

20:13.451 --> 20:16.531
has become so over you see, self-destructive,

20:16.531 --> 20:19.627
that a destruction force is built within himself.

20:21.503 --> 20:26.936
Now think of that force that has built you up into a human

20:27.451 --> 20:29.571
how with care and love,

20:29.771 --> 20:32.571
without your knowledge, without troubling you.

20:32.771 --> 20:35.611
Even when you were born you never knew what was the pain,

20:35.811 --> 20:38.771
of the birth. Your mother took over it.

20:38.771 --> 20:41.491
He's made you a human being

20:41.491 --> 20:46.688
so carefully, delicately he's built you up.

20:47.531 --> 20:48.851
For what?

20:49.491 --> 20:53.829
What is the fruit of this beautiful flower?

20:54.851 --> 20:56.651
Why the flower starts hitting itself?

20:56.851 --> 20:59.981
Have you ever heard of anyone like that?

21:01.771 --> 21:04.331
This is the worst disease, which

21:04.851 --> 21:07.931
we in the West suffer.

21:09.611 --> 21:11.571
French yes,

21:11.851 --> 21:13.731
we had at least double the number of people

21:13.931 --> 21:15.771
that we have here today, surprisingly.

21:15.971 --> 21:18.491
But, also they have the same problem.

21:18.691 --> 21:21.811
And I think all their psychologists,

21:23.011 --> 21:25.011
psychoanalists,

21:25.771 --> 21:28.931
or we can say the, all the books,

21:29.371 --> 21:31.531
all the writers, the philosophers,

21:31.731 --> 21:35.719
everyone has done to them.

21:36.491 --> 21:38.851
They have given these ideas,

21:39.491 --> 21:41.651
and everybody accepts them.

21:42.411 --> 21:45.611
And they curse themselves morning till evening,

21:46.491 --> 21:49.371
walking with so many wrinkles on the forehead.

21:49.971 --> 21:51.651
When you ask them, they will say,

21:51.851 --> 21:54.411
"Mother we are very unhappy people".

21:54.771 --> 22:01.794
It's like asking unhappiness to come and decorate you.

22:02.851 --> 22:10.982
But it has a subtler meaning of which people are not aware.

22:11.811 --> 22:13.851
These are the times,

22:14.851 --> 22:17.611
when you have to get your Realization.

22:17.851 --> 22:20.331
This mass Realization has to work out.

22:20.531 --> 22:22.371
It's all prophesized,

22:22.651 --> 22:25.457
and very important times are these.

22:25.931 --> 22:28.691
All the stars are acting to help us.

22:29.531 --> 22:31.691
The whole universe is helping us.

22:32.851 --> 22:34.971
All the elements are helping us.

22:35.491 --> 22:38.580
We are on the stage.

22:39.771 --> 22:42.371
But when the actors arrive on the stage,

22:42.371 --> 22:44.451
they are finished, they can't act.

22:44.691 --> 22:47.451
They can't do anything, they can't play their game.

22:47.771 --> 22:51.491
They are so involved with their different roles.

22:54.731 --> 22:57.771
And that is why one has to understand the subtler effect of it,

22:57.971 --> 23:00.331
then only you will get rid of this guilt.

23:00.531 --> 23:04.820
You are playing into the hands of negative forces.

23:05.571 --> 23:11.571
They are not less than any atomic bombs,

23:11.571 --> 23:13.411
built within yourselves.

23:14.451 --> 23:15.971
Now what is the way it works out,

23:16.411 --> 23:18.291
I think people do not realize it.

23:18.491 --> 23:20.611
It's a very subtle method.

23:20.851 --> 23:22.451
Let's see the atomic bomb,

23:22.651 --> 23:26.699
hidrogen bomb, what will you do there?

23:27.851 --> 23:30.851
They will separate something which should not be separated.

23:33.651 --> 23:38.691
We break atom, which is not divisible,

23:38.691 --> 23:41.136
into its divisible parts.

23:41.731 --> 23:47.971
So we put a pressure to break them.

23:47.971 --> 23:50.451
And when that breaking force,

23:50.651 --> 23:52.491
that aggression I would say,

23:52.691 --> 23:54.691
is worked out,

23:56.011 --> 23:59.611
that becomes another destructive force.

24:01.491 --> 24:04.531
So whatever effort we have put into that,

24:04.771 --> 24:07.971
multiplies, it's not the same force.

24:09.851 --> 24:13.637
And that we use for our destruction.

24:13.637 --> 24:18.665
I mean, this only human being can do,
to create things to destroy himself.

24:19.371 --> 24:22.651
But this force, which works within our minds,

24:22.851 --> 24:24.731
within ourselves, within our being,

24:24.931 --> 24:28.691
where we actually really hate ourselves sometimes I feel,

24:28.891 --> 24:31.371
the way we are destroying ourselves,

24:32.571 --> 24:33.971
this force

24:34.571 --> 24:36.931
we build within ourselves thanks to  many

24:37.331 --> 24:39.611
nonsensical writers and conditioners

24:39.811 --> 24:44.178
and people who talk of conditioning really condition you much worse!

24:44.571 --> 24:46.931
You should be singing and chanting like a bird.

24:47.931 --> 24:50.731
You should be laughing and enjoying like a flower.

24:51.611 --> 24:53.611
But I find human beings faces,

24:53.811 --> 24:56.731
all, looking so very unhappy.

24:57.851 --> 24:59.731
What's the reason?

25:00.371 --> 25:06.085
The reason is you are separated from your own being,

25:06.771 --> 25:11.651
the being that integrates you. You are completely disintegrated.

25:11.651 --> 25:18.651
When you disintegrate the hidrogen atom

25:18.651 --> 25:21.611
you form a very big force built into it.

25:21.931 --> 25:27.891
In the same way, you are the disintegrating your being:

25:27.891 --> 25:31.651
your physical being on one side, your mental being on another side,

25:31.851 --> 25:37.125
your spiritual being on another side, there's no integrating point.

25:37.731 --> 25:42.113
And when you cannot feel that integration,

25:42.371 --> 25:43.691
you feel guilty,

25:43.891 --> 25:46.571
but that guilt is just a symptom of

25:46.771 --> 25:51.503
a very big destructive force built in you.

25:52.851 --> 25:59.143
This is the way we are going to destroy ourselves.

25:59.771 --> 26:01.451
No other way.

26:01.651 --> 26:04.331
Our destruction is not going to come to us from outside.

26:04.531 --> 26:06.411
That can be controlled.

26:07.371 --> 26:12.780
It's going to come from within, within ourselves.

26:13.611 --> 26:16.851
Everything we do now, after disintegration,

26:17.611 --> 26:26.292
is further disintegration
or further building up that negative force within us.

26:28.011 --> 26:32.242
But to integrate it,

26:32.811 --> 26:36.851
to make you feel complete integration with all your being,

26:38.411 --> 26:40.571
it's only possible

26:41.331 --> 26:43.011
if you can somehow or other

26:43.451 --> 26:45.371
get to that integrating force

26:45.571 --> 26:51.503
which is still there and is quite deep.

26:54.851 --> 26:58.731
That's the last chance, I would say now, that has to work.

26:58.931 --> 27:01.931
The way the negative forces have set in motion

27:02.571 --> 27:05.651
of which you may not be aware at all, you may not be aware,

27:05.851 --> 27:09.851
you don't know what darkness is there.

27:11.531 --> 27:16.411
And to fight it, what one has to do

27:16.571 --> 27:22.311
is to bring that light of the Spirit,
which integrates.

27:22.891 --> 27:24.851
Darkness always disintegrates you.

27:25.411 --> 27:27.731
For example, there's complete darkness, all right,

27:27.931 --> 27:30.931
I can't feel you, I don't know who you are, where you are sitting.

27:31.491 --> 27:32.771
We are all separate.

27:32.971 --> 27:36.391
I can't see you, I don't know who you people are there.

27:36.531 --> 27:39.371
I wouldn't know where is the window, where is the door.

27:39.931 --> 27:42.571
I'll hold this and say, "This is the truth".

27:43.811 --> 27:47.751
All disintegrated personalities,
and disintegrated people,

27:48.411 --> 27:50.771
always see aberrations. They see different things,

27:50.971 --> 27:52.851
different auras, different things.

27:55.971 --> 27:59.971
Now, it's a very vicious circle.
You just think of it.

28:00.651 --> 28:05.351
It's a very great vicious circle we have.

28:05.851 --> 28:14.891
The vicious circle is that we try to think about it,

28:14.891 --> 28:16.651
which is limited.

28:16.851 --> 28:19.891
Supposing I have a limited vision, there's darkness

28:20.531 --> 28:23.262
what will I feel?

28:24.411 --> 28:28.891
You start thinking about it and thinking about it,
pondering over it.

28:28.971 --> 28:34.758
The more you think about it, the worse it becomes.

28:37.611 --> 28:41.371
Another way could be people may try to solve this problem,

28:41.771 --> 28:44.391
to think that we are disintegrated,

28:44.571 --> 28:48.891
is to talk of big things, "We are all brothers and sisters,

28:48.931 --> 28:51.451
let's form U.N. counseling,

28:51.931 --> 28:55.611
let's do world organization".

28:55.851 --> 28:59.291
All blind people doing world organization will end up

28:59.491 --> 29:07.026
at the most, as a labour, what you call, labour department.

29:07.026 --> 29:09.371
That's all.

29:09.891 --> 29:16.931
With all these institutions
working in the big name,

29:17.931 --> 29:19.571
where are we?

29:20.011 --> 29:27.011
Actually, when we become aware, we don't need them.

29:27.011 --> 29:30.282
We don't need at all.

29:31.491 --> 29:34.411
So, this awareness is nothing but

29:34.611 --> 29:38.883
the light of the Spirit within you which is missing.

29:39.411 --> 29:41.571
The Spirit is watching you, all right.

29:41.771 --> 29:43.411
It goes up to a point

29:43.611 --> 29:48.371
to see your stupidity and your limitedness.

29:49.691 --> 29:55.411
And it goes up to a very great extent, I should say,
where it's finished.

29:55.531 --> 29:58.651
It disappears and a person dies,

29:58.931 --> 30:01.691
or he gets into trouble, he becomes creazy, mad,

30:01.891 --> 30:03.331
whatever you may call him.

30:03.531 --> 30:09.391
He develops other diseases like cancer,

30:09.531 --> 30:15.411
which are caused by another problem here,
as you know, Ekadesha.

30:16.011 --> 30:24.398
So, these forces are built within us, of negativity,

30:24.398 --> 30:29.345
when we go to the extremes of negativity.

30:29.891 --> 30:32.011
So, in the Kundalini shastra,

30:32.491 --> 30:38.336
we can say that the left and right side
when used too much,

30:39.451 --> 30:45.771
you build up these forces in the head of eleven Rudras,
the eleven distructive forces.

30:45.771 --> 30:48.571
A cancer patient develops it.

30:48.771 --> 30:52.651
But even before developing cancer,
people can develop it.

30:52.931 --> 30:59.491
And there are so many things,
that can create this,

30:59.851 --> 31:03.531
that sometimes one would feel,
in this vicious circle

31:03.731 --> 31:07.980
that, "How are you going to patch up the whole society?"

31:08.371 --> 31:16.691
And there's only one thing,
that will save the situation, it's Self-realization.

31:18.731 --> 31:27.851
All other things are destroying, are absolutely confusing.

31:28.371 --> 31:31.940
But there's only one thing if you can do,

31:31.940 --> 31:37.030
it saves the whole thing, like putting on the light, finished!

31:38.371 --> 31:43.731
But people don't understand the importance of Self-realization,

31:43.731 --> 31:48.563
because some people ask me, "What's the use of getting the cool breeze in the hand?"

31:48.931 --> 31:52.491
Now, see the big canvas of the whole thing, the whole cosmos,

31:52.491 --> 31:54.537
in a jeopardy.

31:54.537 --> 31:58.531
See what's happening to human beings today.

31:58.531 --> 32:03.811
And if they are to be saved, no use being unhappy.

32:03.811 --> 32:08.731
Like in France they said, "You cannot, Mother, say you are very happy person".

32:08.731 --> 32:10.516
I said, "Why?"

32:10.516 --> 32:17.152
"Because that means you are ignorant of the shocks."

32:17.531 --> 32:20.331
You see, I have to say  "I am very unhappy", you see.

32:20.531 --> 32:22.611
I have to paint some lines here to show you,

32:22.811 --> 32:25.291
that I'm very deeply concerned,

32:25.491 --> 32:29.371
worried about the whole world.

32:29.371 --> 32:31.851
But what is the solution have you got?

32:32.851 --> 32:35.411
You want me to be like you only?

32:35.771 --> 32:37.451
Is that the solution?

32:37.451 --> 32:40.491
That if ten people are weeping you also join them weeping?

32:40.691 --> 32:44.066
Is that the solution?

32:45.691 --> 32:51.971
And the one and only method that we have

32:52.931 --> 32:56.371
which has been already told and prescribed

32:56.451 --> 32:59.851
and has been prophesized,

33:00.931 --> 33:04.571
nobody seeks it.
No one seeks it.

33:04.931 --> 33:07.451
See now, in the Bible: you have to be born again,

33:07.651 --> 33:09.491
Christ is to be born in your heart.

33:09.691 --> 33:12.011
I mean, they do it, even before solving the whole drama

33:12.451 --> 33:14.571
they do it by giving you the second birth,

33:14.771 --> 33:17.371
by Christening you, so called.

33:18.611 --> 33:21.491
Hindus they believe without yoga is there's no sense.

33:21.691 --> 33:24.411
"Yoga kshema vahamyam" Krishna said all the time that,

33:24.611 --> 33:25.691
"You seek yoga". What are you seeking?

33:25.891 --> 33:27.891
All these treatises and all these big books

33:28.331 --> 33:31.331
and all the scriptures are aiming at what?

33:31.651 --> 33:35.661
Even, those who talked, "You must live with dharma
you must live a balanced life"

33:35.661 --> 33:38.411
For what? Why do you do it?

33:38.851 --> 33:40.371
What is the destination?

33:40.691 --> 33:43.851
And the destination is the Spirit.

33:44.611 --> 33:51.551
And today the background is so black,
is so dark,

33:51.651 --> 33:58.351
that this solution is
the end of everything.

33:58.771 --> 34:02.331
But do we realize this?

34:02.851 --> 34:07.811
On the contrary, the vicious circle builts in, within us,
all the time.

34:07.851 --> 34:11.851
"Oh, see how the world is miserable.

34:11.851 --> 34:14.860
Then how can I be happy?

34:16.811 --> 34:18.611
I'm so unhappy in life."

34:18.811 --> 34:21.503
I have yet to come across a person before Realization

34:21.503 --> 34:24.223
saying that, "I am a happy person".

34:25.851 --> 34:29.916
Maybe ego-oriented people might say, "I'm happy",
meaning "my ego is".

34:29.916 --> 34:32.748
You see, if he goes in a swanky car, or something like that,

34:32.748 --> 34:35.491
he's very happy, on top of the world.

34:35.651 --> 34:40.311
After ten minutes, you see him [looking sad]

34:40.811 --> 34:43.371
and this vicious circle is set in.

34:43.571 --> 34:47.351
This ego-oriented circle, or another one, it sets in.

34:47.531 --> 34:50.291
Another vicious circle and another vicious circle

34:50.491 --> 34:52.803
and another vicious circle,

34:52.811 --> 34:54.851
we go on from one to another,

34:54.851 --> 34:58.580
moving on the wheels after wheels,

34:59.531 --> 35:06.531
without realizing that, "Where we are going?"

35:08.571 --> 35:15.391
And this vicious circle has to be broken by one faith,

35:15.391 --> 35:21.811
by one understanding, that God is forgiveness.

35:21.811 --> 35:25.748
God is Love.

35:26.851 --> 35:31.371
When we feel love for anyone, without any lust and greed,

35:31.371 --> 35:35.751
then that is God’s love within us.

35:36.691 --> 35:43.344
That he is the embodiment of that pure love,

35:43.851 --> 35:47.651
which just loves,

35:47.651 --> 35:50.559
which has given you this beautiful human life

35:50.559 --> 35:54.388
and wants to make you more beautiful.

35:55.371 --> 35:57.811
He created all this creation for you

35:58.371 --> 36:03.083
and that he wants you to enjoy the bounties of this creation.

36:03.491 --> 36:06.331
He wants you to enjoy the citizen of his realm

36:06.531 --> 36:11.570
and the Kingdom of his Grace.

36:13.771 --> 36:16.451
Do we go to see someone

36:16.451 --> 36:19.851
who is highly placed, with a morose face? Do we?

36:20.651 --> 36:22.811
That day, we'll specially brush up the hair,

36:23.011 --> 36:25.411
see, make our hair into a beautiful thing,

36:25.611 --> 36:28.524
make our face nice, dress up well,

36:28.524 --> 36:30.880
It looks like we are well, you see.

36:31.851 --> 36:33.851
That’s outside.

36:35.811 --> 36:40.943
Inside, if you just feel how kind he is,

36:42.691 --> 36:47.256
how he has worked out meticulously

36:47.256 --> 36:50.256
in this blissful life of a human being.

36:50.531 --> 36:54.258
But think how much he has done for you!

36:54.531 --> 36:56.651
Instead of that, if you are all the time going to say,

36:56.851 --> 36:58.971
“I am very unhappy in life.”

36:59.411 --> 37:01.611
I mean, think of someone who does everything for you

37:01.811 --> 37:03.331
and you can just come back saying,

37:03.531 --> 37:05.611
“Oh, I am a very unhappy person.”

37:05.811 --> 37:07.371
What is he going to feel about it?

37:07.571 --> 37:09.371
No gratitude.

37:09.731 --> 37:13.001
Count your blessings one by one.

37:13.611 --> 37:14.851
That’s what one has to do,

37:15.451 --> 37:19.462
is to have complete understanding

37:19.462 --> 37:22.314
that he is God Almighty.

37:22.314 --> 37:25.340
He can do anything that he likes.

37:26.371 --> 37:31.962
and we are the recipient of His Allmighty.

37:32.731 --> 37:35.731
He is the Ocean of love,

37:35.931 --> 37:39.851
and we are the recipient of his love.

37:42.771 --> 37:49.068
Let us feel that, within ourselves, and understand logically with wisdom.

37:49.851 --> 37:52.531
If this sets into your mind,

37:52.731 --> 37:55.731
that’s the best conditioning I think human beings can have,

37:57.331 --> 37:59.331
what you call in Sanskrit as  "Susamskara",

37:59.531 --> 38:02.451
means the auspicious conditionings.

38:02.651 --> 38:05.811
You see, we don't have only conditioning and ego.

38:06.011 --> 38:10.985
We have third thing called also good conditioning.

38:11.491 --> 38:15.851
The conditionings that are ruining your chances of enjoyment,

38:16.411 --> 38:18.811
let it be brought round.

38:20.771 --> 38:23.651
And see for yourself, logically you can see

38:23.851 --> 38:28.408
how much is done for you.

38:30.811 --> 38:34.451
I mean none of the animals were that comfortable as you are.

38:34.651 --> 38:36.651
They don't know the idea of comfort. I mean they have never had a car,

38:36.851 --> 38:40.727
even chairs to sit down.

38:43.771 --> 38:46.851
It's easy to say, "Nice to be like animals" you see.

38:46.851 --> 38:49.291
But just go and see the way they live poor things!

38:49.491 --> 38:54.176
No. Even the king of the forest, how he lives, one should go and see.

38:54.891 --> 38:59.215
But he's happy. He's full of joy.

38:59.611 --> 39:01.611
Now he has to kill an animal, he'll kill it,

39:01.811 --> 39:05.367
and with his dignity eat one or two days, finished.

39:05.691 --> 39:07.651
Then he lives for ten days without food.

39:07.851 --> 39:11.011
Whenever he feels hungry he goes, he's not bothered.

39:11.731 --> 39:13.775
He doesn't feel guilty for killing anybody,

39:13.775 --> 39:17.647
he is hungry, he has to eat, he eats, finished.

39:18.971 --> 39:20.971
But human beings, as they are,

39:21.411 --> 39:26.971
they will eat someone without the need, and they'll feel guilty.

39:26.971 --> 39:30.387
This is the problem.

39:33.011 --> 39:36.371
He has made you with his own image.

39:36.571 --> 39:39.740
He's done everything beautifully.

39:40.371 --> 39:43.411
After Realization, you start understanding yourself

39:43.611 --> 39:46.491
and enjoying yourself as you enjoy others.

39:46.491 --> 39:50.124
The fragrance of others you start enjoying.

39:51.691 --> 39:57.851
Self-realization is the only way, you can get the light in.

39:57.851 --> 40:01.971
Enlightenment. Everybody talks of enlightenment, enlightenment.

40:02.451 --> 40:05.971
Enlightenment, means for some people is that you start jumping.

40:07.011 --> 40:10.851
Is it enlightenement to be abnormal like that?
Or take out your clothes?

40:10.851 --> 40:13.451
I mean, just think of it, how does it go into your brains,

40:13.651 --> 40:17.216
I can't understand, that doing all these nonsensical things,

40:17.216 --> 40:20.283
how can there be enlightenment?

40:20.531 --> 40:22.611
Or taking to alcohol, drinking or

40:22.811 --> 40:25.571
drugs or anything. How can it give you enlightenment?

40:25.771 --> 40:29.102
Has it given to anyone so far?

40:29.651 --> 40:32.691
It might be some sort of a funny strange experience  you might get,

40:32.691 --> 40:33.931
but not enlightenment.

40:34.411 --> 40:36.571
In enlightenment, you get integrated,

40:36.771 --> 40:39.291
you see your way through, you know where you are standing

40:39.491 --> 40:42.531
and how you are moving in relationship to others.

40:45.451 --> 40:51.073
So the illogical method, I would say, unwise method,

40:51.073 --> 41:04.254
the way we deal with life, becomes a kind of a possession.

41:06.491 --> 41:11.651
And we are possessed by this negative force which is eating us up.

41:11.651 --> 41:15.971
And we go on living with that idea, enjoing that idea,

41:15.971 --> 41:20.621
that, we are miserable people, we are unhappy, we are helpless.

41:20.623 --> 41:23.602
I mean, I've seen people sitting on the streets and discussing,

41:23.602 --> 41:27.373
"Oh, thank God, there's going to be 8 stars coming in and we'll be all destroyed".

41:27.373 --> 41:31.413
I mean just imagine!

41:32.731 --> 41:35.731
But we have to think about the One who has created us.

41:35.931 --> 41:39.891
Is he waiting for your destruction, will he be happy with that?

41:42.371 --> 41:45.922
How much are you cooperating with Him?

41:46.491 --> 41:51.503
With what care, love, he has created us?

41:51.503 --> 41:53.177
With what hopes whatever it is,

41:53.177 --> 41:54.491
what does he want to do for us

41:54.771 --> 41:56.851
that you are sitting down and feeling guilty?

41:57.371 --> 41:59.571
And now, I have to tell openly,

41:59.771 --> 42:04.083
that it has come to you also through other vechicles,

42:04.691 --> 42:09.157
apart from the psychologists, psychoanalysts.

42:09.411 --> 42:11.811
Psychoanalysts: the other day we had a girl,

42:12.011 --> 42:13.451
she came to see Me.

42:13.651 --> 42:16.651
She's French. Her English was wonderful,

42:16.931 --> 42:18.331
and she said,

42:18.531 --> 42:21.571
"Horrible psychologists! They make me mad."

42:21.771 --> 42:24.611
"Why?" They said, "I have bad relationship with my mother,

42:24.811 --> 42:26.451
I have bad relationship with my father,

42:26.651 --> 42:28.531
bad relationship with every third person".

42:28.731 --> 42:30.811
I don't have that, I've absolutely pure relationship.

42:31.011 --> 42:32.811
They try to put that idea into my head

42:33.011 --> 42:35.411
that there's something abnormal, pathological about me

42:35.611 --> 42:37.558
which I am not!

42:37.811 --> 42:41.298
And they are making my brother's relationship also funny

42:41.298 --> 42:44.801
by telling him that I have bad relations with him.

42:45.691 --> 42:47.396
This is it.

42:47.731 --> 42:49.771
So they hit at the point of pure love,

42:49.971 --> 42:51.691
desintegrate you.

42:51.891 --> 42:54.651
You can't have good relationship with your own mother,

42:54.851 --> 42:58.956
with your own father, with your own sister, with your brother, and nobody.

42:58.956 --> 43:01.571
Because you cannot love except for, you are sex points.

43:01.771 --> 43:03.451
You have just relationship of sex.

43:03.451 --> 43:05.651
Even animals have better relationship then we have,

43:05.851 --> 43:07.931
if you have to accept the psychologists.

43:09.411 --> 43:13.771
And they take money to suggest
all these nonsensical ideas into your head.

43:13.771 --> 43:17.236
There are some here sitting. I will face them later on.

43:19.371 --> 43:22.291
This is how they're putting ideas into your heads

43:22.491 --> 43:27.491
that, "You are a person who has no, no purity

43:27.491 --> 43:28.891
and that you are a sinner,

43:29.331 --> 43:32.651
you are a damned person and any person you look upon,

43:32.851 --> 43:35.651
you have only sex relationships, nothing else.

43:35.851 --> 43:38.819
I mean are we sex points?

43:39.491 --> 43:43.467
With all this evolution God has made us into a sex point:

43:43.467 --> 43:49.432
that's what we have done to ourselves, reduced ourselves to that point only.

43:50.851 --> 43:54.731
He has created you in your own glory and in your own dignity.

43:57.491 --> 43:58.731
He's not created you

43:58.931 --> 44:02.371
to be only wasted like this

44:02.611 --> 44:06.331
Then the second thing that disintegrates us very much more,

44:06.851 --> 44:15.060
is the idea that we are here, you see,
to live in a gross way,

44:15.491 --> 44:19.731
somehow fighting, political, economic,

44:20.531 --> 44:25.811
all these nonsensical progress that we are making.

44:26.491 --> 44:30.793
And everything is explained,
all destructive forces are explained

44:31.046 --> 44:34.651
in the name of political or economic growth.

44:35.371 --> 44:39.611
I don't know if it is 'growth' or whatever it is,

44:39.691 --> 44:42.571
but definetely it is not love, take it from me.

44:42.771 --> 44:45.771
It is not love.

44:46.011 --> 44:51.351
That's why economics of God is to be understood.

44:51.651 --> 44:54.738
Politics of God is to be understood.

44:54.738 --> 44:58.997
And for human beings to understand it, they must have Self-realization.

44:59.531 --> 45:06.311
In his economics, generosity is the key-note.

45:06.811 --> 45:10.902
He enjoys his generosity.

45:11.731 --> 45:17.771
Material things are to express your generosity, isn't it?

45:18.651 --> 45:20.531
What are they for?

45:20.851 --> 45:24.651
The most enjoyable thing is to give,

45:24.851 --> 45:32.851
and when you give, you will see
your economic problems will be solved completely.

45:32.851 --> 45:35.571
Because you are here to become free,  no problems!

45:35.771 --> 45:40.025
The problems are because you want to grab.

45:41.851 --> 45:45.631
And once you start giving, you get it,
as much as you want,

45:45.631 --> 45:50.759
because if there's no outlet, there's no joy,

45:50.759 --> 45:53.679
there's no happiness, there's no release.

45:53.679 --> 45:56.891
from the material domination on you.

45:56.891 --> 45:59.411
But giving is the way

45:59.411 --> 46:02.971
you can get rid of that material domination on your head.

46:03.691 --> 46:05.940
That you give away.

46:07.371 --> 46:08.651
Give away everything that you have

46:08.851 --> 46:13.123
and you'll be surprised how it flows to you.

46:14.651 --> 46:17.491
Now, when I say, "It is fantastic the way it acts.

46:17.691 --> 46:19.611
Fantastic, the way it acts".

46:19.811 --> 46:22.331
Somehow, it’s easy to say,

46:22.531 --> 46:24.371
“It’s Mother is saying something

46:24.851 --> 46:29.651
which is something miraculous.”

46:29.971 --> 46:34.331
But what do you think of Moses
crossing the river, crossing the sea?

46:34.531 --> 46:36.331
You mean, it was miraculous,

46:36.531 --> 46:41.723
or it was a false stoy or what do you think of it?

46:42.531 --> 46:44.891
It was absolutely true,

46:45.371 --> 46:51.200
that he did cross the sea. With the help of God, he could do it.

46:52.651 --> 46:54.891
What about Christ walking on the water?

46:54.891 --> 46:57.451
He did because by his nature, he did it.

46:58.531 --> 47:01.571
What about all the miracles that were done by this Incarnation?

47:01.771 --> 47:07.305
It's absolutely true, I'm here to prove all of them.

47:08.531 --> 47:10.451
But you must get your Realization.

47:10.651 --> 47:12.531
Not because that I cannot prove it,

47:12.731 --> 47:16.771
You must enter into that realm of awareness.
Otherwise, they cannot prove it.

47:16.771 --> 47:19.531
It's true. The other day,
somebody was saying that Rama is a fiction.

47:19.531 --> 47:21.503
I said, "How do you say?"

47:21.851 --> 47:23.491
He said, "Because, it looks like a fiction".

47:23.691 --> 47:27.371
I said, "To human mind, they cannot understand God,

47:27.371 --> 47:31.571
who has millions and millions of hands and eyes

47:31.571 --> 47:33.611
to work out His plans".

47:33.611 --> 47:38.411
So, naturally Rama is a fiction.
Krishna is a fiction. Everybody is a fiction!

47:38.411 --> 47:42.689
Because we ourselves are fictitious, I think.

47:43.811 --> 47:45.971
It's not that it is a fiction

47:45.971 --> 47:49.731
but we are incapable of grasping that is miraculous, which is divine.

47:49.931 --> 47:52.491
and that's why we just call it, "Oh".

47:53.851 --> 47:57.651
No, everything is true, believe me, everything is true.

47:57.851 --> 48:00.371
Now, Rama' s case, let's take it.

48:00.371 --> 48:02.371
Simple to be like Rama, all right?

48:02.851 --> 48:04.531
"Rama is a fiction".

48:04.731 --> 48:08.851
Many of our Indians are very anglicised now, very westernized you see.

48:08.851 --> 48:11.657
So, they want to say, "We don't believe in all these fictions",

48:11.657 --> 48:14.708
so they're becoming English.

48:15.371 --> 48:20.371
For them, to become English is the last epitome,
it's the last word.

48:20.371 --> 48:22.611
"So we don't believe in Rama, nothing, you see." All right,

48:22.811 --> 48:25.651
it's all our old style of thinking.

48:25.651 --> 48:28.371
But he exists and he's within us!

48:28.371 --> 48:32.011
It can be proved with your Kundalini awakening.

48:32.011 --> 48:37.275
The person who has got asthma, who suffers from asthma,

48:37.275 --> 48:40.196
catches on the right heart.

48:40.196 --> 48:44.411
You have to take the name of Rama to cure him.

48:44.411 --> 48:49.851
Nothing else can cure him. It's simple.

48:49.851 --> 48:52.571
The Kundalini stops here.

48:52.771 --> 48:55.411
Many people don't believe in Christ.

48:55.611 --> 49:01.134
"We don't believe in Christ". But you don't believe in Christ, but under what circumstaces?

49:01.134 --> 49:05.574
Why, why don't you believe in Christ?

49:06.411 --> 49:09.975
"Because you see, we don't think he existed, how can it be possible?"

49:09.975 --> 49:14.436
"We don't believe in Moses, we don't believe in Christ, we don't believe in anybody". All right.

49:14.436 --> 49:17.698
Do you believe in yourself?

49:17.698 --> 49:20.505
Perhaps that is missing.

49:20.851 --> 49:24.456
Because the Self is not there.

49:24.456 --> 49:27.576
If you know your Self, you should believe in them.

49:27.576 --> 49:31.411
Because when Kundalini rises, at this point you'll be amazed,

49:31.651 --> 49:34.451
at this point, whether you believe in Christ or not,

49:34.651 --> 49:36.451
at this point,

49:36.651 --> 49:40.411
at the Agnya chakra, where you see the crossing of it,

49:40.411 --> 49:43.491
you have to say Lord's Prayer.

49:43.491 --> 49:46.651
You have to take the name of Christ.
Otherwise, Kundalini doesn't rise.

49:46.651 --> 49:49.411
Now most of the people who are here, who are Realized, know this.

49:49.611 --> 49:52.158
It has been proved to them.

49:52.851 --> 49:57.491
In the Nabhi, in this Void,
if it is hanging, you have to take the name of Moses.

49:57.491 --> 50:01.174
Whether you are a Jew or not, or a hater of Jews
or whatever you may be,

50:01.174 --> 50:06.827
you have to take the name of a Jew, of Moses.

50:07.851 --> 50:12.190
The whole movement of the Kundalini is to intergrate

50:12.190 --> 50:17.851
all the truths which are treated as miraculous,
some people think it's falsehood,

50:17.851 --> 50:19.811
it's good for nothing, useless.

50:20.374 --> 50:25.555
All these things are proved by the movement of the Kundalini

50:25.555 --> 50:28.671
in your central path.

50:29.491 --> 50:35.038
And the greatest of greatest thing
that is proved, is that God exists.

50:35.038 --> 50:38.851
Not only exists but he's active,

50:38.851 --> 50:42.691
that he does everything for us,

50:42.691 --> 50:46.799
that it is he who is the truth and it 's his power of Brahma,

50:46.799 --> 50:49.491
is the truth, the rest is all falsehood and nonsense.

50:50.411 --> 50:54.651
It works in all details too, in small details also.

50:55.851 --> 50:58.331
Now Sahaja Yogis have seen the miracle of Sahaja Yoga,

50:58.531 --> 51:00.331
they cannot explain it.

51:00.531 --> 51:02.651
You cannot explain also.

51:02.651 --> 51:04.611
When you become Realised, you are surprised

51:04.811 --> 51:07.116
how you are helped, how you meet people,

51:07.116 --> 51:09.698
how you get to things, how things work out,

51:09.698 --> 51:13.243
and how it works out so smoothly, you just can't imagine!

51:13.611 --> 51:19.851
Even to the smallest detail it can work out beautifully.

51:19.851 --> 51:23.611
But you have to establish yourself in the kingdom of God.

51:23.811 --> 51:26.463
Not with these fanatical ideas,

51:26.463 --> 51:28.724
like you go to the Catholic church and they say,

51:28.724 --> 51:32.156
"Now you must confess".
I don't know from where did they get this idea!

51:32.156 --> 51:35.674
I don't think Christ would have ever said that,
"You'd better go and confess to these priests",

51:35.674 --> 51:37.834
who are not even Realized souls.

51:38.691 --> 51:42.647
What are they going to do by confession?

51:43.771 --> 51:46.331
And then the answer came to me from a priest.

51:46.531 --> 51:48.651
I've asked him, he's a nice man, he's a Realized soul now,

51:48.851 --> 51:50.891
and he is working for Sahaja Yoga.

51:51.371 --> 51:54.471
But he told me, "The reason is in the Bible it's written,

51:54.491 --> 51:56.451
that, 'Whatever is corrected on this earth,

51:56.651 --> 51:58.551
will be corrected in the heaven'.

51:58.651 --> 52:00.651
That's why you'd better correct it by telling to the priest."

52:00.851 --> 52:03.511
Now, by any logical means do you think these priests

52:03.531 --> 52:07.651
can help you by telling them anything?

52:08.491 --> 52:13.771
Whatever is to be correced
on this earth is your Kundalini and your chakras.

52:14.651 --> 52:18.091
If the language of the Bible has been,

52:18.331 --> 52:19.811
especially the Old Testament,

52:20.011 --> 52:25.371
has been extremely guarded, it was security measure.

52:25.371 --> 52:29.771
Like the Tree of Life
is nothing but the Kundalini which is enlightened.

52:29.771 --> 52:33.571
Absolutely, it is that, it looks like that, like a tree.

52:33.771 --> 52:35.971
The other day, we were having program - I think today only,

52:36.411 --> 52:38.651
my children showed me, "Look, the Kundalini".

52:38.851 --> 52:42.371
I went and saw they were describing about Moses something,

52:42.371 --> 52:45.196
perhaps, and this was the Tree of Life, they said.

52:45.196 --> 52:49.244
And my children, grandchildren said, "See, the Kundalini".

52:50.611 --> 52:57.371
The language they used, may be for security measures made,

52:57.371 --> 53:01.411
but not the word,

53:01.411 --> 53:05.491
if it is now changed by human beings, it's false.

53:05.491 --> 53:08.491
Human beings can change words, that's a different point,

53:08.691 --> 53:11.851
but you can see, in Sahaja Yoga you can see what is changed,

53:12.331 --> 53:15.571
what is wrong, which is falsehood. You can see all these things.

53:15.771 --> 53:17.531
So, to disintegrate you,

53:17.731 --> 53:21.571
these things are again created in the name of religion, so-called.

53:22.517 --> 53:24.288
I mean these people are there for God

53:24.288 --> 53:27.377
or for making you feel guilty?

53:27.731 --> 53:33.451
Like, say Jews think that Christ was not a saviour.

53:33.451 --> 53:38.303
If they are still waiting for two hundred years. It's not true.

53:38.691 --> 53:41.771
He's the One, without Him you cannot raise the Kundalini.

53:41.971 --> 53:44.771
One should understand that he's the Mahavishnu described.

53:45.274 --> 53:46.954
But if I say something,

53:46.954 --> 53:49.451
that doesn't mean that you should believe Me. Not at all.

53:49.451 --> 53:52.611
But you should see for yourself because if you are interested,

