What is the approach towards the Christian Church?

01:11:44.971 --> 01:11:46.331
What is it?

01:11:46.531 --> 01:11:50.371
What it's our approach, the line, for the Christian Church?

01:11:50.371 --> 01:11:53.566
Have pity for them.

01:11:57.731 --> 01:12:02.182
You see, I took my birth in the Christian religion, in India,

01:12:02.851 --> 01:12:05.651
and first, the Hindus, you see, they were very upset

01:12:05.851 --> 01:12:10.495
that, "How could She take birth in a Christian religion?"

01:12:10.495 --> 01:12:13.606
I mean, so-called Christian religion.

01:12:13.851 --> 01:12:21.503
And I must tell you, I was baptized forcibly by a Lutheran Church.

01:12:21.503 --> 01:12:24.326
All right?

01:12:25.571 --> 01:12:32.394
The simple answer is that Christians are the most fanatic people.

01:12:32.771 --> 01:12:36.503
And the Indian Christians are the worst

01:12:36.503 --> 01:12:40.122
because they think Christ was born in England.

01:12:40.651 --> 01:12:43.451
Really they think so. You see, if you have an English name

01:12:43.651 --> 01:12:46.451
then you are a real Christian. Otherwise, you are not.

01:12:46.451 --> 01:12:49.851
You can't imagine how ignorant they are.

01:12:49.851 --> 01:12:53.851
And how the Christans are most fanatic. It looks funny but it is so.

01:12:54.691 --> 01:13:00.451
Because their fanatism is so beautifully managed.

01:13:00.451 --> 01:13:03.851
It is not like Khomeini is, which is stark open fanaticism.

01:13:04.651 --> 01:13:08.571
You know, Khomeini is that and he has to accept he is.

01:13:08.571 --> 01:13:13.491
But this way it is very well polished, you know, beautifully done.

01:13:13.491 --> 01:13:16.677
Others can be said they are stones

01:13:16.677 --> 01:13:19.491
but this is like a diamond artificially made.

01:13:19.851 --> 01:13:24.973
They do social work this Christian way.

01:13:24.973 --> 01:13:27.611
Now for example, if you ask somebody the way in England,

01:13:27.811 --> 01:13:30.263
it's a Christian way to tell the way, you see.

01:13:30.371 --> 01:13:33.771
What God has got to do with this?Just tell me.

01:13:33.771 --> 01:13:35.691
They have mixed up God with all these things,

01:13:35.891 --> 01:13:38.451
it's such a big mixture they have made,

01:13:38.451 --> 01:13:43.859
that the fanaticism of Christianity is very much in delusion.

01:13:45.771 --> 01:13:52.550
For them, begging in the name of God is also Christian.

01:13:53.491 --> 01:13:55.617
It's a very dangerous game,

01:13:55.617 --> 01:13:58.811
because they are the cleverest of all, they think.

01:13:58.811 --> 01:14:02.371
So, the way they have entangled themselves into,

01:14:02.851 --> 01:14:07.491
it's so much dogmatic and so beautifully philosophised.

01:14:07.851 --> 01:14:09.851
It's a philosophy.

01:14:09.851 --> 01:14:12.531
To know it, you have to get out of it.

01:14:12.531 --> 01:14:17.702
It is so beautiful, you can't imagine. It's so beautiful.

01:14:18.491 --> 01:14:23.849
And so appealing, they are the most kindest people,

01:14:23.849 --> 01:14:28.719
compassion personified, great people, Christians.

01:14:28.719 --> 01:14:32.594
And the Christains believe it. Christ never asked you to beg.

01:14:33.456 --> 01:14:36.651
He never asked you to collect money for the poor.

01:14:36.851 --> 01:14:41.137
Nothing of the kind. It was not his idea at all, you see.

01:14:41.491 --> 01:14:43.651
He wanted you to get your Realization.

01:14:43.851 --> 01:14:46.438
That's what he wanted.

01:14:46.771 --> 01:14:49.651
You have created the poor.

01:14:49.651 --> 01:14:53.611
And you'd better look after them. That's not God's job.

01:14:53.611 --> 01:14:56.491
Communists may be the greatest Christians, like that,

01:14:56.771 --> 01:14:59.491
the way they look after their poor.

01:14:59.851 --> 01:15:04.782
God's job is one: is to give you Realization. Not other one.

01:15:06.331 --> 01:15:12.489
To take you away from this ignorance and mire of life,

01:15:13.851 --> 01:15:17.901
into that beautiful, blissful, kingdom of God.

01:15:17.901 --> 01:15:21.503
That is the work of God.

01:15:21.651 --> 01:15:24.371
And not these things which you describe back.

01:15:24.571 --> 01:15:29.524
But it looks so idealistic, you know,
the whole thing is such an idealism.

01:15:30.331 --> 01:15:32.491
That's why it's very, very dangerous.

01:15:32.691 --> 01:15:36.503
And it's so well organized.

01:15:38.371 --> 01:15:42.611
So well organized, you know, so well organized.

01:15:42.611 --> 01:15:47.011
Even the hymn numbers, everything is done so well,
every book done so well.

01:15:47.011 --> 01:15:51.503
Stand up to sing. Now you sit down.
So regimented, beautifully.

01:15:51.651 --> 01:15:54.256
No one can realize even that this is,

01:15:54.256 --> 01:15:56.851
we are going all to madness, you see.

01:15:56.851 --> 01:15:59.851
It's a very wonderful thing.

01:16:00.531 --> 01:16:02.731
You are not supposed to look this side or that side.

01:16:02.931 --> 01:16:05.811
It's all right. In England, I have Christians,

01:16:05.811 --> 01:16:07.931
many have been Christians, you see.

01:16:08.371 --> 01:16:10.737
I have Christians, Jews, all kinds of disciples.

01:16:10.737 --> 01:16:14.971
Indian Christians, I don't have even one. Except for,
of course, my family people are from there,

01:16:14.971 --> 01:16:16.931
but they've known my childhood, they know me.

01:16:17.371 --> 01:16:21.945
But the rest of them, for them I am a healer!

01:16:24.331 --> 01:16:28.332
I am, believe me!

01:16:30.651 --> 01:16:35.065
Hindus are my disciples, then Muslims are. But not Christians.

01:16:35.491 --> 01:16:40.227
Not one, I knew this.

01:16:41.851 --> 01:16:49.782
And when I went to America,
they pronounced, "A Christian mystic has come".

01:16:49.782 --> 01:16:53.972
That gave me good marks, you know.

01:16:55.371 --> 01:16:59.396
People came to see me because I was a Christian mystic,

01:16:59.396 --> 01:17:05.906
properly baptized. I must get my certificate also.

01:17:08.851 --> 01:17:13.651
So our attitude should be of simply pity towards them.

01:17:13.651 --> 01:17:16.531
Like Blake has said, "The priest cursed,

01:17:17.451 --> 01:17:20.291
cursed my head when he baptized me."

01:17:20.491 --> 01:17:22.416
It's something like that, it is really.

01:17:22.416 --> 01:17:24.651
We should have really simple pity for all the people,

01:17:24.851 --> 01:17:28.651
who go to churches where there are all the graves.

01:17:28.851 --> 01:17:32.651
They sit on the graves, take all the spirits into themselves.

01:17:32.851 --> 01:17:35.497
God save them.

01:17:38.851 --> 01:17:46.321
I don't know why Christians, everyone is just like that.

01:17:49.011 --> 01:17:52.491
But, among the Christians only, I am sure,

01:17:52.731 --> 01:17:57.498
one day Sahaja Yoga will come up very well.

01:17:58.531 --> 01:18:07.509
That's the power of Christ. I hope so.
I hope so.

01:18:10.491 --> 01:18:15.431
Mislaid, and misled people also,

01:18:15.691 --> 01:18:18.371
who are enjoying that misleading

01:18:18.371 --> 01:18:21.491
are most difficult, aren't they?
Don't you think so?

01:18:21.531 --> 01:18:24.611
How can you talk to them?

01:18:24.611 --> 01:18:27.851
Who can break it?

01:18:33.491 --> 01:18:36.451
When I go to India, I can speak,

01:18:36.771 --> 01:18:42.491
in a 'sanathana', means Catholic,
'sankar sanathana' means Catholic temple,

01:18:42.691 --> 01:18:45.651
where thousands of people came to attend my lecture

01:18:45.851 --> 01:18:48.651
and they respect me as a saint.

01:18:48.651 --> 01:18:51.931
Do you think in any church whatsoever,

01:18:52.491 --> 01:18:54.411
I would be respected like that,

01:18:54.411 --> 01:18:57.651
except for one "Unity Church" we had,

01:18:57.651 --> 01:18:59.771
where all kinds of bhoots are respected.

01:18:59.771 --> 01:19:03.331
So, I was also called to give a lecture.

01:19:03.851 --> 01:19:09.731
It was I think more of a - I don't know,
money-making proposition whatever it was.

01:19:09.731 --> 01:19:12.458
Whatever it was.

01:19:13.611 --> 01:19:17.531
But in India, that's the blessing

01:19:17.771 --> 01:19:19.811
of the Hindus that they are not organized.

01:19:20.011 --> 01:19:23.371
For them, a saint is a saint.

01:19:24.371 --> 01:19:32.681
Even the Prime minister, even, I would say, the president

01:19:32.681 --> 01:19:37.826
of India would stand for a saint. They wouldn't sit.

01:19:39.651 --> 01:19:42.397
These ideas are not here.

01:19:42.651 --> 01:19:47.951
We're too organized to get out of this organized way,

01:19:47.951 --> 01:19:52.023
to find out what is beyond. You see, we just -

01:19:52.023 --> 01:19:55.610
all our spirituality is satisfied by going to Sunday church,

01:19:55.610 --> 01:19:58.900
finished! Or to give some money for the feat. That's all.

01:19:58.900 --> 01:20:00.451
That's not the way it is.

01:20:00.651 --> 01:20:02.731
It's much, much, much more.

01:20:03.851 --> 01:20:06.691
But be kind to them.

01:20:07.451 --> 01:20:11.851
Christ has said, "You'll be calling me, 'Christ, Christ'.
I won't recognize you"

01:20:11.851 --> 01:20:18.849
That's what they are. I'm sorry for them, really sorry.

01:20:22.851 --> 01:20:24.975
Any other question?

01:20:26.491 --> 01:20:29.491
Mother, can everybody become aware at the most

01:20:29.491 --> 01:20:31.491
how do you recognize them up?

01:20:31.691 --> 01:20:34.531
Yes, everybody can.

01:20:34.771 --> 01:20:37.611
But everybody doesn't mind, want it.

01:20:37.851 --> 01:20:42.456
You see, they don't want it. See how many people are here.

01:20:43.731 --> 01:20:46.451
But if it was some sort of a falsehood,

01:20:46.451 --> 01:20:48.651
if I'd come with two horns,

01:20:48.651 --> 01:20:52.303
there could have been three halls big like this.

01:20:53.371 --> 01:20:56.571
People don't want reality, my child, they don't want it.

01:20:56.851 --> 01:20:58.851
They never wanted it.

01:20:59.491 --> 01:21:01.491
They always crucified it.

01:21:02.851 --> 01:21:05.651
But now, at least, there are some who really want it.

01:21:05.851 --> 01:21:08.611
And I am happy you think of others also,

01:21:08.611 --> 01:21:11.001
very happy to know that.

01:21:12.275 --> 01:21:16.155
But it’s a difficult task.

01:21:16.811 --> 01:21:20.243
I have to work very hard.

01:21:21.491 --> 01:21:24.451
They don't want reality
because in Sahaja Yoga it is a becoming,

01:21:24.651 --> 01:21:26.731
It is not just to come and fill in a form,

01:21:26.931 --> 01:21:31.541
"All right, you are the member", or you pay supposing a one-pound, a membership fees.

01:21:31.541 --> 01:21:35.411
It's not that! It's your becoming, what you become!

01:21:35.411 --> 01:21:39.771
It's your thing, that must happen. You must get your properties.

01:21:39.771 --> 01:21:43.065
This is the problem.

01:21:46.371 --> 01:21:49.439
You have to give up a little bit.

01:21:49.439 --> 01:21:52.546
It's easy to give up.

01:21:53.731 --> 01:21:56.491
It's very easy but I never talk about it before Realization,

01:21:56.691 --> 01:21:58.651
because after Realization, you just give up.

01:21:58.851 --> 01:22:00.411
If I tell you, half of you might go away,

01:22:00.411 --> 01:22:02.721
so I'm not going to tell you.

01:22:02.721 --> 01:22:05.598
You'd better get your Realization. It will work it out.

01:22:05.598 --> 01:22:08.851
It will establish a new priority within yourself, naturally.

01:22:08.851 --> 01:22:11.860
Because if you have light you see.

01:22:12.491 --> 01:22:14.851
You see snake as snake and rope as rope.

01:22:15.651 --> 01:22:19.952
So, I don't have to tell you,
you just see it, you just feel it, it happens to you.

01:22:20.611 --> 01:22:22.651
Yes, I know, I know. I wish I could.

01:22:22.851 --> 01:22:26.286
It can be done to all the new people,

01:22:26.286 --> 01:22:28.841
whatever race you may belong; it can.

01:22:28.841 --> 01:22:31.667
But how many are there?

01:22:32.851 --> 01:22:34.651
It's a very slow movement.

01:22:34.851 --> 01:22:39.001
For four years, I had only seven Britons with me.

01:22:39.001 --> 01:22:44.812
I was struggling with them. Four years, can you imagine? In England.

01:22:48.651 --> 01:22:50.754
It's tremendous task.

01:22:51.851 --> 01:22:54.451
All right. So, you get your Realization now.

01:22:54.451 --> 01:22:56.860
Let's see how many you bring in.

01:22:58.691 --> 01:22:59.771
Yes?

01:23:00.771 --> 01:23:05.899
Divine Holy Mother, after Self-realization,

01:23:05.899 --> 01:23:09.297
how long it takes for a new [unclear]

01:23:09.297 --> 01:23:12.929
is it possible to stop reincarnating and seek perfection?

01:23:13.451 --> 01:23:17.611
Is it easy? Last, what did he say? What d'you say?

01:23:20.851 --> 01:23:23.891
Is it easy to? Last sentence, what do you say?

01:23:24.371 --> 01:23:27.651
I was saying after Realization, is it possible

01:23:27.851 --> 01:23:30.651
to stop reincarnating

01:23:30.851 --> 01:23:35.651
and to be perfect in these troubled times?

01:23:35.851 --> 01:23:40.256
You are reincarnated by Self-realization itself.

01:23:41.851 --> 01:23:44.371
And to stop having rebirth and birth?

01:23:44.571 --> 01:23:47.531
You don't think of these things afterwards.

01:23:47.531 --> 01:23:53.066
Because you are not futuristic anymore. You live in the present.

01:23:54.571 --> 01:23:56.611
You see these ideas of rebirth and

01:23:56.811 --> 01:23:59.451
this frightening stuff: you should not have rebirth.

01:23:59.691 --> 01:24:00.912
Why not?

01:24:02.491 --> 01:24:07.011
I mean, you create a beautiful house, everything,

01:24:07.491 --> 01:24:11.405
and then you say that you don't live in it?

01:24:11.851 --> 01:24:16.771
When you become a rich man, you want to enjoy your wealth isn't it?

01:24:16.771 --> 01:24:19.651
But they're not Buddha's saying:

01:24:19.851 --> 01:24:22.651
birth is suffering, death is suffering.

01:24:22.851 --> 01:24:26.371
Yes, that's true, but not Realization.

01:24:32.731 --> 01:24:34.931
You see, what he has said is:

01:24:35.491 --> 01:24:37.491
Buddha never asked you to

01:24:37.491 --> 01:24:41.928
to limit your desire of ascent.

01:24:41.928 --> 01:24:43.611
Because people talk of God, once

01:24:43.811 --> 01:24:46.971
they talked of it in India but nobody talked of the deities.

01:24:46.971 --> 01:24:50.491
That was a problem, because it became a talk again.

01:24:50.491 --> 01:24:55.411
Then they talked of a God which was abstract,

01:24:55.411 --> 01:24:59.048
like you can say, Jehova and other things,

01:24:59.377 --> 01:25:03.851
because they wanted people to get over their

01:25:03.851 --> 01:25:08.491
stuck-up points you see. Nothing worked you see.

01:25:08.491 --> 01:25:13.023
So Buddha said, "All right, let's talk only about
the Self-realization, nothing else. Not even of God.

01:25:13.075 --> 01:25:18.366
Let's talk of that.
Let people get to Self-realization, then we'll talk about God.

01:25:19.451 --> 01:25:23.558
So, he said, "All right. Only Self-realization. No God, nothing."

01:25:23.891 --> 01:25:28.157
That was his job. Fix you up with the idea of Self-realization.

01:25:28.491 --> 01:25:32.531
He said, "Dont' worship anything, don't worship, get your Self-realization.

01:25:32.531 --> 01:25:38.210
They are worshipping everything under the sun, these Buddists!

01:25:38.851 --> 01:25:41.694
What am I to do?

01:25:44.034 --> 01:25:50.118
So whatever Buddha has said,
everything is re-said in Sahaja Yoga.

01:25:52.771 --> 01:25:54.771
“Buddham sharanam gachami.”

01:25:55.811 --> 01:25:59.565
I surrender myself to the enlightened One.

01:25:59.851 --> 01:26:04.458
The One which is enlightened is your Spirit.

01:26:05.691 --> 01:26:07.811
“Sangham sharanam gachami,”

01:26:08.011 --> 01:26:10.895
I surrender myself to the collectivity.

01:26:10.895 --> 01:26:13.678
Unless and until you are a collectively conscious person,

01:26:13.678 --> 01:26:15.967
how can you surrender?

01:26:17.491 --> 01:26:21.503
Buddha also, whatever he said,
is not understood before Realization. You cannot.

01:26:21.503 --> 01:26:23.996
“Dharmam sharanam gachami,”

01:26:23.996 --> 01:26:26.020
is the sustanance within us.

01:26:26.020 --> 01:26:28.571
'Sharanam' means you become that.

01:26:28.571 --> 01:26:31.331
It's not a mental thing, "Oh, I surrender myself".

01:26:31.531 --> 01:26:34.339
But you just become.

01:26:36.571 --> 01:26:38.651
You become the enlightened one.

01:26:38.851 --> 01:26:41.541
You become the collectively conscious.

01:26:41.541 --> 01:26:45.590
You become the dharma, the sustenance, the religion within us.

01:26:45.590 --> 01:26:47.590
You become!

01:26:47.851 --> 01:26:49.651
That's what he meant.

01:26:49.851 --> 01:26:54.060
But for them, 'Sharanam gachami' means take a wheel in the hand, go on

01:26:54.060 --> 01:26:56.731
"Buddham sharanam gachami".

01:26:56.731 --> 01:27:01.161
Now. What this wheel is going to do, I just don't understand, you know.

01:27:01.811 --> 01:27:04.331
They'll go on hours together, they'll go mad.

01:27:04.531 --> 01:27:07.691
They will end up into lunatic asylum, beieve me.

01:27:08.851 --> 01:27:12.371
Or like mad you have to say something, all the time praying.

01:27:12.371 --> 01:27:15.411
Is that the way you are becoming?

01:27:15.851 --> 01:27:20.001
They don't even know where is Buddha placed into yourself.

01:27:24.851 --> 01:27:28.252
But Sahaja Yogis know where he is placed

01:27:28.252 --> 01:27:30.122
and how to please him.

01:27:30.531 --> 01:27:37.375
Whatever he said is nothing but Sahaja Yoga, absolutely 100%

01:27:40.811 --> 01:27:46.366
Actually, Buddha was nobody else but an Incarnation,

01:27:46.366 --> 01:27:49.590
who reincarnated himself as Adi Shankaracharya.

01:27:49.590 --> 01:27:51.503
You can see it clearly in your being,

01:27:51.503 --> 01:27:53.331
it can be proved on Kundalini again!

01:27:53.331 --> 01:27:56.304
You see, how can I prove it?

01:27:59.851 --> 01:28:02.651
To understand them, first you get your Realization.

01:28:02.851 --> 01:28:07.097
Again, I am talking like Buddha only.

01:28:09.331 --> 01:28:14.120
He tried something
by which he thought people will take to Realization.

01:28:14.851 --> 01:28:17.316
But human beings as they are...

01:28:18.411 --> 01:28:20.611
He thought they are very much involved in materialism,

01:28:20.811 --> 01:28:23.851
take them out, try this, try that. Nothing works out.

01:28:24.411 --> 01:28:26.531
Nothing.

01:28:26.531 --> 01:28:31.609
Only thing that works out: the real happening, nothing else.

01:28:36.771 --> 01:28:39.506
Mother, you are [inaudible]?

01:28:39.851 --> 01:28:41.371
What's it?

01:28:42.851 --> 01:28:45.721
Say it loudly.

01:28:50.651 --> 01:28:53.606
All right?

01:28:55.851 --> 01:28:59.731
Is there somebody else saying something which I didn't hear?

01:28:59.931 --> 01:29:03.771
Today, the vibrations are so much that really, to be very franck,

01:29:04.811 --> 01:29:06.291
you can't imagine!

01:29:06.503 --> 01:29:08.663
I don't know how I'm listening to you, what you are talking.

01:29:08.851 --> 01:29:11.451
It's really too much flowing out.

01:29:11.651 --> 01:29:13.731
I can't believe it. Why?

01:29:13.931 --> 01:29:17.195
There must be some great seekers
who must have come today.
